title: Firestorm - Vol. 1
description:
Take a high school jock and a award winning scientist and throw in a nuclear powered bomb and mix them all together and what do you get? 

Firestorm the Nuclear Man!!! Able to change the atomic properties of anything that is non-organic, Firestorm first burst onto the DC Comics scene in 1978 and the character (if not the same people) have been lighting the worl on nuclear fire ever since!

I hope this works! This collection includes Firestorm v1, his DC Comics Presents and Brave and the Bold appearances, his JLA joining issue, the cancelled comic cavalcade issue #6 as well as the Flash v1 back-ups! Enjoy this and please seed.

Tony
